title: DM Protection (rewrite only)
description:
A cog that blocks every user that advertises a discord server in the first private message of your conversation with him (Also marks the message as read).
You can toggle the dmprotect with
- `dmprotect/dmp`

[(Check the Source Code)](https://github.com/Bluscream/Discord-Selfbot-Cogs/blob/master/dmprotect.py)
